title: Intervention S07E10 - Chad and Brooke Follow-Up
description:
Meet Chad, a former Postal Service Cycling Team member. Chad met crack. Watch Chad come back.
Meet Brooke, a person with lots of medical problems. Brooke met prescription paid medication. Brooke met lots of prescription pain medications. Watch Brooke come back, but still with lots of medical problems.

It's the Intervention Follow-Up Episode! Season 7, Episode 10.
We all love to see the drama of addiction. Here's the drama after treatment.
